tlaps-bench bundles TLA+ specifications adapted from third parties. Comments are
removed from the synthesis-from-scratch task copies; the protocols and proof
obligations are unchanged. Original copyright and license notices are retained
below.

benchmark/synthesis-from-scratch/etcd_raft
    Derived from the raft TLA+ specification in etcd
    (https://github.com/etcd-io/etcd).
    Copyright 2024 The etcd Authors.
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0; a copy is available at
    http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
    Bundled library modules (Folds, Functions, SequencesExt, FiniteSetsExt,
    BagsExt, Relation, and their *Theorems variants) come from the TLA+
    CommunityModules (https://github.com/tlaplus/CommunityModules, MIT).

benchmark/synthesis-from-scratch/AbstractRaft
    A high-level TLA+ abstraction of the Raft consensus protocol
    (Diego Ongaro and John Ousterhout, "In Search of an Understandable
    Consensus Algorithm", USENIX ATC 2014).

benchmark/synthesis-from-scratch/tlaplus_examples_GermanProtocol
    The German cache-coherence protocol, imported from tlaplus/Examples
    (https://github.com/tlaplus/Examples, MIT).
